<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Length_bounds">Length bounds</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Longest_increasing_subsequence&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Length bounds"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>According to the <a href="/wiki/Erd%C5%91s%E2%80%93Szekeres_theorem" title="Erdős–Szekeres theorem">Erdős–Szekeres theorem</a>, any sequence of <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle n^{2}+1}">
