  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1b0744bc6c0cbdf56197698229110e29b06cb8a9" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.505ex; width:6.452ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle n^{2}+1}"></span> distinct integers has an increasing or a decreasing subsequence of length <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle n+1.}">
